# Finding: RBP-F002
# RBP-004: CrateId newtype triplicated across portability/runtime/boundary without validation
# Phase: phase-A | Mode: initial_pass | Triaged: 2026-05-10T00:00:00Z

<urn:atm:triage:finding/RBP-F002>
  a triage:Finding ;
  triage:findingId "RBP-F002" ;
  triage:title "RBP-004: CrateId newtype triplicated across portability/runtime/boundary without validation" ;
  triage:description "CrateId newtype is defined independently in crates/sc-lint-portability/src/lib.rs:28, crates/sc-lint-runtime/src/lib.rs:31, and crates/sc-lint-boundary/src/lib.rs:94 without validation in the portability/runtime versions. RBP-004 requires shared types to be defined once. The portability and runtime versions lack the format invariant validation (debug_assert non-empty) and the Display/AsRef/Deref impls present in the canonical boundary definition." ;
